OL,3,CPuffin numbers hit 'record high' on
OL,4,Csmall Welsh island vital for the
OL,5,Cseabirds
OL,7,FA record number of puffins have been
OL,8,Frecorded on Wales's Skomer Island, an
OL,9,Finternationally important island for
OL,10,Fseabirds, conservationists have said.
OL,12,FThe Wildlife Trust of South and West
OL,13,FWales (WTSWW) said it had recorded
OL,14,F52,019 puffins in this year's count on
OL,15,Fthe island off the coast of
OL,16,FPembrokeshire, beating the previous
OL,17,Frecord of 43,626 set last year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
