OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776957067
OL,3,CPuffin numbers hit 'record high' on
OL,4,Csmall Welsh island vital for the
OL,5,Cseabirds
OL,7,FThe figures have been unveiled
OL,8,Ffollowing the annual count, which sees
OL,9,Fa team of conservationists setting out
OL,10,Fon a calm, clear evening in spring
OL,11,Fwith binoculars and notepads to count
OL,12,Fevery puffin on land, in the sky and
OL,13,Fthe sea.
OL,15,FThe count has to be timed right in the
OL,16,Fseason to ensure the bulk of birds
OL,17,Fhave returned but before they are
OL,18,Fsettled on eggs in their burrows,
OL,19,Fwhere they would be out of sight.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776957067
OL,3,CPuffin numbers hit 'record high' on
OL,4,Csmall Welsh island vital for the
OL,5,Cseabirds
OL,7,FThe method used to count the birds,
OL,8,Fwhich are red-listed in the UK over
OL,9,Fconservation concerns and designated
OL,10,Fas "vulnerable" to extinction globally
OL,11,Fby the International Union for the
OL,12,FConservation of Nature (IUCN) Red
OL,13,FList, is the same as wardens have used
OL,14,Fon the island since the 1980s.
OL,16,FThis means the data can be compared
OL,17,Facross more than 40 years, the team
OL,18,Fsaid.
