CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776957067
OL,3,CPuffin numbers hit 'record high' on
OL,4,Csmall Welsh island vital for the
OL,5,Cseabirds
OL,7,FLeighton Newman, Skomer Island warden
OL,8,Ffor the wildlife trust, said that
OL,9,Fafter numbers of seabirds washed up on
OL,10,Fbeaches across southern Europe earlier
OL,11,Fthis year, the team had not expected a
OL,12,Fcount as high as the one they had
OL,13,Ffound.
OL,15,F"It's a very pleasant surprise to see
OL,16,Fthe puffin population thriving," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@`O]
