PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776957067
OL,3,CPuffin numbers hit 'record high' on
OL,4,Csmall Welsh island vital for the
OL,5,Cseabirds
OL,7,F"Puffin numbers are declining at many
OL,8,Fsites around the UK, but Skomer bucks
OL,9,Fthe trend ` and it's thanks to long-
OL,10,Fterm monitoring work that we know this.
OL,12,F"It's special that Skomer is a refuge
OL,13,Ffor so many seabirds, and it's a
OL,14,Fprivilege to be able to work to
OL,15,Fprotect them, but we want to see
OL,16,Fseabird populations thriving across
OL,17,Fthe UK."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@HO]
