OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776957067
OL,3,CPuffin numbers hit 'record high' on
OL,4,Csmall Welsh island vital for the
OL,5,Cseabirds
OL,7,FWTSWW said the increase in the puffin
OL,8,Fpopulation on the island was likely
OL,9,Fdue to an abundance of food in the
OL,10,Farea, with plenty of fish for chicks
OL,11,Fleading to high breeding success and
OL,12,Fhelping good numbers of adults survive
OL,13,Fover winter.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
