PN,46407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1776957067
OL,3,CPuffin numbers hit 'record high' on
OL,4,Csmall Welsh island vital for the
OL,5,Cseabirds
OL,7,FSkomer's bird populations, which also
OL,8,Finclude guillemots, razorbills,
OL,9,Fkittiwakes and fulmars that breed on
OL,10,Fthe cliffs around the island, also
OL,11,Fbenefit from the absence of rats and
OL,12,Fother predators that pose a threat to
OL,13,Fseabirds nesting on other UK islands
OL,14,Fwhere they are not naturally found but
OL,15,Fhave been introduced.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/8
